                        SHADOW OF THE BEAST 2

TYPED IN BY PARASITE OF LSD.


THE CONFLICT CONTINUES.....
Your deadly struggle for freedom against the dark forces of the beast
lord is now but a painful memory. You try to forget the anguish of the
past by concentrating on your prize for success in th bloody battle,
the return of your humanoid body.

But as you slowly adjust to your newly-won phisique, the pain you
thought gone is now about to return... The beast mage has kidnapped
your sister! She must be rescued before she falls foul of his dark
arts. You journey to a hostile alien world to face the maleviolent
hosts of the beast mage and interact with more friendly characters to
learn of your unfamiliar surroundings.

You must fight your way through many enemy-infested levels collecting
and using weapons and objects to ade your crusade towards conflict
with the beast mage... Before he makes your sister his own!

CONTROLS:
Use a joystick in port 2.
F1-F4 Use item.
F10 Quit game.
A - Ask question
O - Offer
S - Score

Some weapons have a limited use.

CHEAT MODE:
When the game starts, go right, when you meet the man in the woods, press
(A) for Ask and type TEN PINTS. You now have infinite energy.
